cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques, specifically superpixel segmentation and matching. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel descriptor and matching framework, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. The paper also involves multi-scale matching, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves searching for similar descriptors, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
